import React from 'react';
import {
  Nav,
  NavLink,
  Bars,
  NavMenu,
} from './Navele';

const Navbar = () => (
  <>
    <Nav>
      <Bars />

      <NavMenu>
        <NavLink>
          Home
        </NavLink>
        <NavLink>
          Trending Task
        </NavLink>
        <NavLink>
          My Tasks
        </NavLink>
        <NavLink>
          My Updates
        </NavLink>

      </NavMenu>

    </Nav>
  </>
);

export default Navbar;
